import { ReactElement } from 'react'; export function Awards(): ReactElement { return ( <>

Awards and Honors

  • Sep. 2016: FicFinder {' '} received ACM SIGSOFT Distinguished Paper Award in ASE 2016 [ News link]
  • Jul. 2016: Elite was evaluated as{' '} Platinum Artifact in FSE 2016
  • May 2016: Prof. Shing-Chi Cheung received{' '} Distinguished Reviewer Award in ICSE 2016
  • Apr. 2016: CSNIPPEX {' '} was accepted as Evaluated Artifact in ISSTA 2016
  • Jan. 2016: Chang Xu received{' '} CCF Young Computer Scientist Award [ Certificate]
  • Oct. 2015: Ming Wen received{' '} School of Engineering (SENG) PhD Fellowship Award, SENG HKUST, 2014-2015.
  • Sep. 2014: GreenDroid {' '} was selected as the feature article of TSE in the issues of September 2014 [ News link]
  • Sep. 2014: Chang Xu received{' '} ACM Nanjing Rising Star Award [ Certificate]
  • Nov. 2014: Yepang Liu received ACM SIGSOFT Service Recognition Award at FSE 2014 [ Certificate ]
  • Nov. 2014: Yepang Liu received ACM SIGSOFT Service Award at FSE 2014 [ Certificate ]
  • Jul. 2014: CrashLocator {' '} received ACM SIGSOFT Distinguished Paper Award in ISSTA 2014 [ News link ]
  • Jul. 2014: SHAP received Best Paper Award{' '} from APSEC 2014 [Certificate]
  • May 2014: PerfChecker{' '} received ACM SIGSOFT Distinguished Paper Award in ICSE 2014 [ News link] [ Certificate]
  • Sep. 2012: Chang Xu received CVIC SE Talents{' '} [Certificate]
  • Sep. 2011: Chang Xu received{' '} National Science and Technology Progress Award (Second Class, 7/10) {' '} [ Certificate ]
  • May 2011: Chang Xu received{' '} New Century Excellent Talents in University by the Ministry of Education
); }
